title: Undekhi
overview: Show depicts the two aspects of the society - the power-drunk influential people who think they can get away with anything and the oppressed, subjected to years of torture, who finally decide to bring themselves to justice

tv.episodeOverview: Ghosh interrogates Saloni and team to Rinku’s chagrin and finds discrepancies in their stories. Meanwhile, the wedding festivities continue. Teji confronts Daman about the shooting. Saloni cracks a deal with Rinku in exchange for Rishi’s silence.
